-- 01_deduplicated_billing.sql
```sql
CREATE TEMP TABLE deduplicated_billing AS
SELECT DISTINCT ON (subscription_id, event_month)
    event_id,
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount,
    event_type
FROM billing_events
ORDER BY subscription_id, event_month, event_id;
```

-- 02_monthly_subscription_metrics.sql
```sql
SELECT
    b.event_month                                  AS month,
    COALESCE(p.tier, 'Unknown')                    AS tier,
    COALESCE(c.industry, 'Unknown')                AS industry,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.subscription_id)              AS active_subscriptions,
    SUM(b.amount)                                  AS total_mrr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id)                      AS unique_users
FROM deduplicated_billing b
JOIN subscriptions s  ON s.subscription_id = b.subscription_id
LEFT JOIN plans p     ON p.plan_id = s.plan_id
LEFT JOIN users u     ON u.user_id = s.user_id
LEFT JOIN companies c ON c.company_id = u.company_id
WHERE s.status = 'active'
GROUP BY b.event_month, COALESCE(p.tier, 'Unknown'), COALESCE(c.industry, 'Unknown')
ORDER BY b.event_month, tier, industry;
